{"tid":572790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平稱帝 中國必有內亂","createTime":"2018-02-26T01:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T02:20:34.000Z","uid":168158,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"81317d69d227662298b6237d7733c14f003d2d7f","tid":572790,"uid":168158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T01:23:32.000Z","msg":"其實習近平唔算係一個英明領袖，經濟搞到一塌糊塗，唔少實業俾佢玩死，增長主要靠房地產，但係無實業嘅增長就好似水中花一樣，一有大壇野即刻收皮，家下佢用印銀紙戰術頂住，根本係治標不治本，先勿論呢樣野。所謂打貪腐只不過係打壓異己，清算政敵嘅手段，成班人仲話去係一代明君<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後一帶一路，洗咗幾千億，仲柒過香港堆大白象，結果得到嘅只係啲垃圾國家嘅支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 英美錢就收咗，實際上暗地繼續耍手段整垮一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後稱帝係違反全世界民意，就算強如普京都要做門面功夫，扮下民主先上位，家下習總對外國就奶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，內部就係咁打壓成班開國元老同前任領導人嘅利益集團，內部未平何以稱帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，加上咁明顯地反民主，打算改終身制，好難令人唔令歐美有藉口係中國搞三搞四<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  結果就係內外夾攻，中國係將來會係不久嘅將來出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大家小心睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e02c0857950f03aea0fb5a602360d001e84367c","tid":572790,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T01:31:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6037a3222e3913cc387c9c76103ebe1fcb1c7bd","tid":572790,"uid":15358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T01:32:53.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"d686703eb2cf1515b34c24bdf0df0e52a4cc104d","tid":572790,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:13:20.000Z","msg":"最好出事啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4c75ab78cbfc3e20034e7bd274b41fee2c05ff","tid":572790,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/101504_f502b6b6152b8129066b2bbc5833df01.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F101504_f502b6b6152b8129066b2bbc5833df01.gif&h=618b1cfe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42ca6a587a719bef63d0fe46ab842a8d48bebae4","tid":572790,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:20:34.000Z","msg":"內就唔會出事<br />\n支那人出名奶皇<br />\n邊會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}